dct_description_sm: from Mr. Arrowsmith's Chart of the Pacific Ocean ; Sy. Hall sculpt., 14 Bury St Bloomsbury.
Includes note on Kerguelan [sic] and Amsterdam islands, and map of New Zealand.
Macquarie River only Australian mainland feature, with note:"Macquarie Rivr. supposed to flow across the continent to the west coast."
